title: There are places where the veil
description: There are places where the veil between worlds thins, and secrets wash ashore. Your journey leads to just such a locale: Clementine's Beach. It is imperative that you explore Clementine's Beach, for within its tranquil embrace lies something forgotten, waiting to be rediscovered by those with keen eyes.

trailLocation.title: Clementine's Beach
trailLocation.description: A beautiful beach perfect for relaxation, swimming, and water activities.
